f\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />個個都唔知有咩行動<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />對唔對得住烈士同被捕手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>星期五 <span style=\"color: red;\">獅子山之路</span> 7:30 樂富 <br />\n</strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9KQxrNJ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9KQxrNJ.png&h=c869dffa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>星期六 <span style=\"color: red;\">天水圍親子遊行</span> 2:30 天秀公園</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/O0LtKzJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FO0LtKzJ.jpg&h=85f2aac9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>星期日 <span style=\"color: red;\">金鐘民陣遊行</span> 2:30 東角道</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/09/12/185803_2cefd2fa1345b60607d92f6a90928d20.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F09%2F12%2F185803_2cefd2fa1345b60607d92f6a90928d20.png&h=a89435a1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n幫手做文宣同連儂牆<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e4ff9cb5674b7f607fa3c2c85e21af1dad5de81","tid":1560491,"uid":271250,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T12:42:58.000Z","msg":"無拍成個禮拜<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6bcc6365cf11545e3a26286d9b9112cdef872ec2","tid":1560491,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T13:42:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/smile.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11f4eb15b16d413fb817f8c33491182c48cff3dc","tid":1560491,"uid":20898,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T13:47:53.000Z","msg":"全月通坐輕鐵，都唔拍出入閘"},{"pid":"d85f99265b5e6832f2bb8323d1275461027279a0","tid":1560491,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T21:17:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/smile.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3bbea899fe438df3f012909d8fb85905fb8288c","tid":1560491,"uid":75148,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T21:39:35.000Z","msg":"如果我有嘟卡 我一定屌撚完佢地一獲先比佢地查<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n你老母個臭閪 封撚曬D售票機我點撚樣買飛呀 你咁撚驚人爆你機 你個個站搵人去睇撚住丫麻 你估個撚個都有八達通架<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02a48edc5c55e1bf46a47903734739b7eaad3417","tid":1560491,"uid":123713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T21:40:08.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">913中秋要人!!</span></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/L6Tnu54.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FL6Tnu54.jpg&h=d1f0aa7d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n公海<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/NBHSAUrkFTtbziGhzabb2g\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FNBHSAUrkFTtbziGhzabb2g&d=33lQL0pOg%2F%2Bbj%2F%2FH3PrIWSlkmYPKinjppKJkD7WQ61o%3D&h=b3807ff8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/NBHSAUrkFTtbziGhzabb2g</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">各區集合地點!</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n油麻地、佐敦、尖沙咀: 梳士巴利公園(太空館附近)<br />\n荃灣、大窩口、青衣: 荃灣公園(海濱長廊)、青衣海濱長廊<br />\n葵興、葵芳、荔景: 林士德遊樂場、葵涌運動場<br />\n美孚: 嶺南之風<br />\n太子、旺角: 花墟公園<br />\n荔枝角、長沙灣: 長沙灣遊樂場<br />\n深水埗: 通州街公園<br />\n油塘、藍田: 油塘道遊樂場<br />\n將軍澳、寶琳、坑口、康城<br />\n中西區（西區、中環、金鐘、半山、山頂）<br />\n灣仔、銅鑼灣、天后、炮台山: 維園中央草坪<br />\n鰂魚涌、太古、西灣河、筲箕灣: 沿海旁<br />\n小西灣、杏花邨、柴灣: 柴灣公園<br />\n鑽石山、黃大仙: 黃大仙廣場<br />\n九龍灣、牛頭角、觀塘: 觀塘海濱公園<br />\n大圍、沙田、馬鞍山 : 沙田百步梯<br />\n元朗、天水圍: 天水園公園<br />\n屯門: 屯門公園<br />\n南區: 鴨利洲風之塔公園<br />\n<br />\n仲有獅子山同山頂人鏈!"},{"pid":"15071787ec381063ccc5a95c80808e1d136ef8c0","tid":1560491,"uid":198097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T21:57:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"267d9ea4f4d12c10e3bffef9f68355be8a13ac2c","tid":1560491,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T00:25:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/smile.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"421df7021da65e67e3d0f1795bd87cb1f21cddaf","tid":1560491,"uid":5420,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T00:28:42.000Z","msg":"有日真係唔小心本能咁拍左卡<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14f468ce058c0c9fd0000b644b92fbd24fa800ad","tid":1560491,"uid":279391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T00:32:10.000Z","msg":"冇拍卡"},{"pid":"4f6974f81be696779ef118b0e36ae2f12274ed24","tid":1560491,"uid":53612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T00:34:47.000Z","msg":"趕時間 跑走 唔駛查"},{"pid":"cd8cc5310f62dbf5a223b9e1add6611beea72f73","tid":1560491,"uid":179414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T00:49:50.000Z","msg":"雖然都係有啲怯但呢排都無拍卡"},{"pid":"b172970a728c5b47e41299dda8f3af7204445231","tid":1560491,"